[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それでは第１回九偉人会、開始しまーす！\nみんな、召し上がれ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00972",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "山奥の村なのに魚もあるのか、\nランツェのおじさまのおかげだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00973",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "うまい！　うまいぞ、ナナ！\n素材の味を感じるぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_00974",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヴァレリアらしい、野生を感じる料理ですね。\n味より量に対するこだわりを感じます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_00975",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "美味しいものがいっぱいで嬉しいってことかしら？\nふふ、やったわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00976",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ほら、ヘルトも食べて！\n美味しいわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00977",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00978",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者、食べないのなら我にくれ！\n我はもっと食べて、もっと強くなるのじゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00979",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょっとゼロ！　これはヘルトのよ！\nっていうか、この会の目的忘れたの？！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00980",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヴァレリアのご飯は美味しいけど、\nヘル兄の様子は変わらないね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00981",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "無言、無表情で食べてて、なんだか気味悪いよ。\nこれ食べ終わったら、僕は帰らせてもらうから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00982",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "これは一家団らんの食事会なのですよ！\n独りで席を立たないでください！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_00983",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "魚かぁ……\n骨多くて、ちょっと苦手……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00984",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "骨、鋭くて危険。\n私が排除する",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00985",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ありがとう、ヤド姉！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00986",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ねえヘルト、ご飯、美味しい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00987",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00988",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "どれが一番美味しい？\nこれ？　それともあれ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00989",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00990",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……ねぇ、ちょっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00991",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様は、まだ本調子ではないようですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_00992",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "うーん。これは重症だね。\n腹が膨れても元気にならないなんて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00993",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "じゃ、食べ終わったし僕は帰るよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00994",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょっ、待ってよシトリン！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00995",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "やだよ。元々僕は乗り気じゃないし、\n怖いヘルトと同じ場所になんかいたくないんだってば",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00996",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "前から思ってたんだけど、シトリンは\nどうしてそんなにヘルトが怖いのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00997",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトだって、きっと何か理由があって\nシトリンにきつく当たってるのかもしれないわよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00998",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "そんなの知らないよ。そもそもヘルトが何を\n考えてるのかなんて分からないんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00999",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ヘルトが何を考えているのか……\n　どんなことを思うのか、私にも分からない）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01000",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（普段のヘルトって、どういう人なのかしら）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01001",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]